msgstr "ນັດໝາຍເບິ່ງຕົວຢ່າງການໃຊ້ງານ"

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select the <b>vendor</b> and <b>expected delivery date</b>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <b>ຜູ້ສະໜອງ</b> ແລະ <b>ວັນທີຈັດສົ່ງທີ່ຄາດໄວ້</b>."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Set the inventory <strong>route to \"Manufacture\"</strong> for all "
"manufactured products."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ <strong>ເສັ້ນທາງຄັງສິນຄ້າເປັນ \"ການຜະລິດ\"</strong> ສຳລັບຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ຜະລິດເອງທັງໝົດ."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Since Odoo is not a design tool, all necessary drawings must be created in a"
" dedicated drawing program."
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກ Odoo ບໍ່ແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືອອກແບບ, ແບບຜັງທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດຕ້ອງຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນໂປຣແກຣມອອກແບບສະເພາະ."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Speed up the signing process thanks to the <strong>Sign</strong> app. Once "
"again, all the signed documents will be stored in the "
"<strong>Documents</strong> app."
msgstr ""
"ເລັ່ງຂັ້ນຕອນການເຊັນເອກະສານດ້ວຍແອັບ <strong>ເຊັນ (Sign)</strong>. ເອກະສານທີ່ເຊັນແລ້ວທັງໝົດຈະ"
"ຖືກເກັບໄວ້ໃນແອັບ <strong>ເອກະສານ (Documents)</strong>."

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Starting a construction project implies a lot of important documents such as"
" contracts, building plans, instructions for use, subcontracting agreements,"
" etc. Instead of scattering them in your emails, storage services or "
"computer, attach them in the chatter and they will be automatically "
"centralized in the <strong>Documents</strong> app."
msgstr ""
"ການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໂຄງການກໍ່ສ້າງມີເອກະສານສຳຄັນຫຼາຍຢ່າງ ເຊັ່ນ: ສັນຍາ, ແບບຜັງອາຄານ, ຄຳແນະນຳການນຳໃຊ້, ສັ"
"ນຍາຈ້າງເໝົາຊ່ວງ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ. ແທນທີ່ຈະປ່ອຍໃຫ້ພວກມັນກະຈັດກະຈາຍຢູ່ໃນອີເມວ ຫຼື ຄອມພິວເຕີ, ໃຫ້ຄັດຕິດພວກມັນ"
"ໄວ້ໃນກ່ອງສົນທະນາ ແລະ ພວກມັນຈະຖືກລວມສູນໄວ້ໃນແອັບ <strong>ເອກະສານ</strong> ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: carpenter
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:carpenter.project_project_1
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "ໜ້າວຽກ"

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <b>Manufacturing and Inventory app</b> is designed to help you manage "
"your in-house production and keep a close eye on the stock levels of your "
"raw materials."
msgstr ""
"<b>ແອັບການຜະລິດ ແລະ ຄັງສິນຄ້າ</b> ຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອຊ່ວຍທ່ານຄຸ້ມຄອງການຜະລິດພາຍໃນ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມລະ"
